quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,3,aur ( logon ne ) is ke siwa aur mabood bana liye hain jo koi cheez bhi peda nahi kar saktay aur khud peda kiye gay hain. aur nah apne nuqsaan aur naffa ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhtay hain aur nah marna un ke ikhtiyar mein hai aur nah jeena aur nah mar kar aُth kharray hona
  25,4,aur kafir kehte hain ke yeh ( quran ) mann gharat baatein hi jo is ( mudai risalat ) ne banali hain. aur logon ne is mein is ki madad ki hai. yeh log ( aisa kehnay se ) zulm aur jhoot par ( utar ) aeye hain
  25,5,aur kehte hain ke yeh pehlay logon ki kahaniyan hain jis ko is ne likh rakha hai aur woh subah vsham is ko parh parh kar sunai jati hain
  25,6,keh do ke uss ne uss ko utaara hai jo asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ko jaanta hai. be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  25,7,aur kehte hain ke yeh kaisa paighambar hai ke khata hai aur baazaaron mein chalta phirta hai. kyun nazil nahikiya gaya is ke paas koi farishta is ke sath hadaayat karne ko rehta
  25,8,ya is ki taraf ( aasman se ) khazana utaara jata ya is ka koi baagh hota ke is mein khaya karta. aur zalim kehte hain ke tum to aik jaadoo zada shakhs ki pairwi karte ho
  25,9,( ae paighambar ) dekho to yeh tumahray baray mein kis kis terhan ki baatein karte hain so gumraah hogaye aur rasta nahi paskte
  25,10,woh ( khuda ) bohat babarkat hai jo agar chahay to tumahray liye is se behtar ( cheezein ) bana day ( yani ) baagaat jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hon. neez tumahray liye mehal banade
  25,11,balkay yeh to qayamat hi ko jutlatay hain aur hum ne qayamat ke jhutlanay walon ke liye dozakh tayyar kar rakhi hai
